metadata.name: HANDS OF PEACE
metadata.description:
We can make peace with our own hands regardless of out ages, nationality, sex, skin color, professions, abilities… Peace in the world, peace in mind, peace around are the result of our activities, our actions and efforts we can put in. The hands are the symbol of deeds, actions, work… 
"Hands of peace" is the artworks to show that we all can make a peace.
